task.summary: 添加第一个 js 事件
添加第一个 js 事件
现在知道了client js 和 server js 的区别，需要 client js 请求数据到 server 然后 server js 才运行，index js 就是 server部分，而分离的 http 却是 client js
start get post method from client
add request npm, will find dom parse npm
add cheerio; jquery selector 没有弄好，找了半天，原来是 missing the '#'
first get dom from the website
server js (index.js) can not import local js home.js
css without mui, or just mui
add div to warp the existed item
mui list accessoryType can modify ，table view cell padding and mui navigate right padding，and after:: padding
mui refresh , the refresh wrapper scroll div must id = pullrefresh can scroll
